dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jordan Garcia. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Jordan. My name is Beverly White.
Great to meet you, Beverly! Could you please provide me with the license plate number of the vehicle involved in the incident?
Of course, it's Bravo Bravo Four Five Charlie.
Thank you, Beverly. Can you also confirm the date of the accident?
The incident occurred on the fifteenth of November, two zero two three.
Thank you for the information, Beverly. We will process your claim and keep you updated on the progress. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Jordan.
You're welcome, Beverly. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
